text: Ivanovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Aydaralinsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 2 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 17 km from Sterlibashevo, 5 km from Aydarali. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Ivanovka, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
